Test the Envenom yourself before asking about any change: as I said, I don't want to rock that boat.  I agree that you should not be able to wear items to get to 50 env, apply Lifebane, and then take them all off... but I am 99% positive it doesn't work that way.  Poisons 2 or more levels below someone's level will proc for them regardless of their Env skill, or even if they have it at all (non-assassins).<br>
